Dalawang taon na ang nakalilipas,

00:14:19.520 --> 00:14:20.400
Nag-fellowship ako

00:14:20.420 --> 00:14:21.400
sa Songshan nang mahigit isang taon.

00:14:22.400 --> 00:14:23.540
Bakit hindi kita nakasalubong noon?

00:14:24.440 --> 00:14:25.700
Kailan ka eksaktong naroon?

00:14:25.800 --> 00:14:26.600
Mayo bago ang huli.

